{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "6f2a9d4c-7b3e-4a1f-9c6d-2e5b8f0a1c4d",
    "name": "TaxVision - Connectors",
    "description": "Coleccion del microservicio Connectors de TaxVision (OAuth Gmail/Graph, IMAP, Watch API, push webhooks, body/attachment fetch M2M). Usa el environment TaxVisionBackEnd (UrlBase apunta al Gateway, p. ej. http://localhost:5047). Los endpoints de Messages son M2M puro (policy ServiceOnly, claim actor_type=Service) — el {{accessToken}} debe venir de POST /auth/service-token (ver coleccion Auth), no de un login de usuario.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Accounts",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Initiate",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"providerCode\": \"Gmail\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/accounts",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "accounts"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Arranca el flujo de conectar cuenta (D3 §12.4). `providerCode` es `Gmail` o `Graph` (para IMAP usar `POST /connectors/accounts/manual`, este endpoint no aplica). Genera un `state` CSRF de un solo uso y devuelve `{ authorizationUrl }` — el frontend redirige el navegador ahi (no es un fetch normal, el consentimiento vive en Google/Microsoft). Requiere connectors.accounts.write."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 200 with authorizationUrl, or documented error\", () => {",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property(\"authorizationUrl\");",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    pm.expect([400, 403]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "  }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "ConnectManual",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"emailAddress\": \"contacto@miempresa.com\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Contacto MiEmpresa\",\n  \"imapHost\": \"imap.miempresa.com\",\n  \"imapPort\": 993,\n  \"imapUseSsl\": true,\n  \"imapUsername\": \"contacto@miempresa.com\",\n  \"imapPassword\": \"{{connectorsManualImapPassword}}\",\n  \"smtpHost\": \"smtp.miempresa.com\",\n  \"smtpPort\": 587,\n  \"smtpUseStartTls\": true,\n  \"smtpUsername\": \"contacto@miempresa.com\",\n  \"smtpPassword\": \"{{connectorsManualSmtpPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/accounts/manual",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "accounts",
                "manual"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Conecta una cuenta manual IMAP+SMTP (D3 Compose §8) — sin redireccion, valida conectividad real contra ambos servidores (`IManualAccountConnectivityValidator`) antes de persistir nada. Si `emailAddress` ya esta conectado bajo otro tenant o el mismo tenant, falla limpio sin tocar la DB (desconectar primero). Requiere connectors.accounts.write."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 200 with accountId, or documented error\", () => {",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property(\"accountId\");",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property(\"emailAddress\");",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    pm.expect([400, 403]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "  }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "List",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/accounts",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "accounts"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista las cuentas de correo conectadas del tenant (`TenantEmailAccountDto[]` — nunca incluye el token/credenciales). Requiere connectors.accounts.read."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 200 with array, or documented error\", () => {",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an(\"array\");",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    pm.expect([403]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "  }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GetById",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/accounts/{{connectorsAccountId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "accounts",
                "{{connectorsAccountId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Detalle de una cuenta conectada (`TenantEmailAccountDto` — nunca incluye el token). Requiere connectors.accounts.read."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 200 with id, or documented error\", () => {",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property(\"id\");",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    pm.expect([403, 404]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "  }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Disconnect",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/accounts/{{connectorsAccountId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "accounts",
                "{{connectorsAccountId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Desconecta la cuenta: revoca la OAuthConnection y, para Gmail, intenta ademas revocar el refresh token del lado de Google (best-effort, POST oauth2.googleapis.com/revoke) — Graph no tiene API equivalente, el usuario debe revocar el consentimiento el mismo desde myaccount.microsoft.com/consents. Requiere connectors.accounts.write."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 204 or documented error\", () => [204, 403, 404].includes(pm.response.code) || pm.expect.fail(\"Got \" + pm.response.code + \": \" + pm.response.text()));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "AdminConsentUrl",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/accounts/admin-consent-url",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "accounts",
                "admin-consent-url"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Fallback de admin-consent para Graph (D3 §12.6) — solo util cuando el connect normal (Initiate) fallo con AADSTS90094/consent_required. Devuelve `{ url }`: un admin del tenant de Microsoft lo visita para otorgar consentimiento a nivel organizacion. La mayoria de los tenants nunca lo necesita. Requiere connectors.accounts.write."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 200 with url, or documented error\", () => {",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property(\"url\");",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    pm.expect([403]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "  }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Reauth",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/accounts/{{connectorsAccountId}}/reauth",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "accounts",
                "{{connectorsAccountId}}",
                "reauth"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Reintenta el setup de watch/subscription de una cuenta tras TenantEmailAccount.Status == Error (renewal agoto reintentos, o el OAuth grant se revalido fuera de banda). Requiere connectors.accounts.write."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 204 or documented error\", () => [204, 400, 403, 404, 409, 502].includes(pm.response.code) || pm.expect.fail(\"Got \" + pm.response.code + \": \" + pm.response.text()));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Webhooks",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GmailPush",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{connectorsGmailPushJwt}}",
                "type": "text",
                "description": "JWT real emitido por Google Pub/Sub (Google.Apis.Auth valida la firma) — no hay forma de simular esto sin un push real de Gmail."
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"message\": {\n    \"data\": \"eyJlbWFpbEFkZHJlc3MiOiJvZmZpY2VAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaGlzdG9yeUlkIjoxMjM0NX0=\",\n    \"messageId\": \"1234567890\"\n  },\n  \"subscription\": \"projects/x/subscriptions/y\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/webhooks/gmail-push",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "webhooks",
                "gmail-push"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Publico — Pub/Sub push de Google. Decodifica el envelope base64 ({emailAddress, historyId}), resuelve TenantEmailAccount por email, fetch history y publica connectors.raw_message_received.v1 por cada mensaje nuevo (solo metadata, nunca body). Rate limit 100 req/min por IP. Devuelve 200 incluso si la cuenta no existe (no-retryable); 500 en otros fallos para que Pub/Sub reintente."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "GraphNotification",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"value\": [\n    {\n      \"subscriptionId\": \"sub-id\",\n      \"clientState\": \"{{connectorsGraphClientState}}\",\n      \"resource\": \"me/mailFolders('inbox')/messages\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/webhooks/graph-notification",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "webhooks",
                "graph-notification"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Publico — Microsoft Graph subscription notification. Con ?validationToken=xxx en el query string responde el eco text/plain (handshake de creacion de subscription). Sin eso, valida clientState en tiempo constante contra Connectors:Watch:Graph:ClientState (rechaza 401 si el secreto no esta configurado o no matchea) y procesa el delta. Rate limit 100 req/min por IP."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Messages (M2M)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GetBody",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tenantId\": \"{{tenantId}}\",\n  \"accountId\": \"{{connectorsAccountId}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/messages/{{connectorsProviderMessageId}}/body",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "messages",
                "{{connectorsProviderMessageId}}",
                "body"
              ]
            },
            "description": "M2M — solo Correspondence (u otro microservicio backend), nunca frontend ni usuario final. Fetch bajo demanda del body completo del mensaje (html/text/headers/attachments metadata, sin bytes de attachments). Timeout 30s, rate limit 10 req/min por (tenant, accountId). Requiere policy ServiceOnly (claim actor_type=Service)."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 200 or documented error\", () => [200, 403, 404, 429, 502, 504].includes(pm.response.code) || pm.expect.fail(\"Got \" + pm.response.code + \": \" + pm.response.text()));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GetAttachment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tenantId\": \"{{tenantId}}\",\n  \"accountId\": \"{{connectorsAccountId}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/messages/{{connectorsProviderMessageId}}/attachments/{{connectorsAttachmentId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "messages",
                "{{connectorsProviderMessageId}}",
                "attachments",
                "{{connectorsAttachmentId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "M2M — solo Correspondence. Fetch bajo demanda del binario del attachment (streaming, Content-Type + filename resueltos via GetMessageAsync, nunca confia en metadata del caller). Rate limit 5 req/min por tenant. Requiere policy ServiceOnly (claim actor_type=Service)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Send",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"tenantId\": \"{{tenantId}}\",\n  \"subject\": \"Re: Documentacion fiscal 2025\",\n  \"html\": \"<p>Hola, adjunto la documentacion solicitada.</p>\",\n  \"text\": \"Hola, adjunto la documentacion solicitada.\",\n  \"to\": [\"cliente@ejemplo.com\"],\n  \"cc\": [],\n  \"bcc\": [],\n  \"replyToDisplayAddress\": \"Contador TaxVision <contacto@miempresa.com>\",\n  \"inReplyToInternetMessageId\": null,\n  \"references\": null,\n  \"replyToProviderMessageId\": null,\n  \"attachments\": [\n    {\n      \"filename\": \"factura.pdf\",\n      \"contentType\": \"application/pdf\",\n      \"contentBase64\": \"JVBERi0xLjQKJcOkw7zDtsO...\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{UrlBase}}/connectors/accounts/{{connectorsAccountId}}/send",
              "host": [
                "{{UrlBase}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "connectors",
                "accounts",
                "{{connectorsAccountId}}",
                "send"
              ]
            },
            "description": "M2M (D3 §3.7, unico consumidor hoy: ConnectorsSendClient en Postmaster, README 35.8) — envio saliente via la cuenta OAuth/IMAP+SMTP conectada. El token del proveedor nunca sale de Connectors: recibe un OutboundMessage normalizado (nunca MIME crudo, Graph no lo acepta para crear un envio nuevo) y lo traduce a la forma nativa (GmailApiClient/GraphApiClient/SmtpManualClient). `attachments[].contentBase64` es el contenido en base64 (D3 Compose §16 Fase 1). Sin threading real en v1: `inReplyToInternetMessageId`/`references`/`replyToProviderMessageId` son opcionales. Timeout 30s en el HttpClient del proveedor, rate limit 20 req/min por (tenant, cuenta) via ISendRateLimiter. Requiere policy ServiceOnly (claim actor_type=Service)."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"status 200 with providerMessageId, or documented error\", () => {",
                  "  if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property(\"sentAtUtc\");",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    pm.expect([400, 401, 403, 404, 429, 504]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "  }",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
